Minimum financial Requirements: Minimum ATO (Annual Turnover) of any one year during last five audited financial years from comprehensive maintenance must not be less than 4 Crore. Tenderer shall submit last five years audited financial statement (Profit Loss Statement) duly attested / certified by CA.			Audit report of 2016-17 to 2020-21,to be indexed at the rate of 8% for a year.

Company/Firm  Documents The contracting firm/agency shall be a well established and reputed firm specialised in the trade and registered as a legal entity for a minimum period of 5 years and having experience and capacity in the execution of similar works			memorandum and articles of association of the firm should be submitted.
